<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Johann I. von Egloffstein, Bischof von Würzburg</head><p>Der Rat bittet, dem Popp Hödlein, Armmann des Gerhard Zollner, Bürger zu Nürnberg, das Erbe seines in Heidingsfeld verstorbenen Bruders Eiring Hödlein folgen zu lassen.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_66" id="32v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_66_r3l1">Bẏſchoff cʒu VVircʒburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_66_r3l2">Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Vns hat fürgelegt / Gerhart cʒollner <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r3l3">Burger / vvie daʒ Jm popp hödlein von Staffelſtein ſein Armman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r3l4">geſagt hab / daʒ her Eyring Hödlein ſein pruder cʒu heẏtingſfelt von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r3l5">tods wegen abgangen ſeẏ / vnd etwieuil habe gelaſſen hab / der Er </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r3l6">nehſter erb ſeẏ / darein Jm <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hochwirdıkeit ein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pote</expan> vnd <expan>bekümeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r3l7">gelegt hab / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> Armenmann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r3l8"><expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habe darcʒu Er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> recht hat / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wılle<ex>n</ex></expan> onhinder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r3l9">nüſſe volgen laſſen wöllet / Als etc / das <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vigılia<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_66_r3l10">/ <expan>b<ex>ea</ex>ti</expan> <expan>Tho<ex>m</ex>e</expan> <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan> / Anno . ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_66" id="32v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Byschoff czu Wirczburg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnediger <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Gerhart Czollner,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> burger, wie daz im Popp Hödlein von Staffelstein, sein
            armman, gesagt hab, daz her Eyring Hödlein, sein pruder, czu Heytingsfelt von tods wegen
            abgangen sey und etwievil habe gelassen hab, der er nehster erb sey; darein im
                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hochwirdikeit ein <expan>v<ex>er</ex>pote</expan> und
                <expan>bekümeru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> gelegt hab. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz
            ir dem <expan>egen<ex>an</ex>t<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>s</expan> armenmann <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habe, darczu
            er <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> recht hat, durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> on hindernüsse volgen lassen wöllet, als etc. Das
                <expan>wolle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                <expan>vigilia<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>ea</ex>ti</expan>
<expan>Tho<ex>m</ex>e</expan>
<expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan> anno ix<hi rend="sup">o</hi>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
